Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.30,0:00:16.12,OP,,0,0,0,,大廈的外牆 巨大的銀幕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.15,0:00:26.75,OP,,0,0,0,,都會的女神 KISS KISS KISS 對我笑 SO SWEET I FOUND YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.55,0:00:33.60,OP,,0,0,0,,一億個夢 會有十億個機會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.62,0:00:41.42,OP,,0,0,0,,肯定對的路 NO NO NO沒人會知道 DON'T CHEAT
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.33,0:00:50.72,OP,,0,0,0,,迷宮般的道路 只有我與你兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.74,0:00:57.27,OP,,0,0,0,,CARRY ON CARRY ON 嘗試走出一步的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.86,0:01:00.78,OP,,0,0,0,,CAN'T STOP IT NO WAY OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.85,0:01:03.66,OP,,0,0,0,,CAN'T STOP IT 永遠地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.69,0:01:12.33,OP,,0,0,0,,CAN'T STOP IT 停不下來 HOW CAN YOU HOLD ME ON？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.52,0:01:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,珊璞在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.00,0:01:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,珊璞，你在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,最少回答我一聲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.54,0:01:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,珊璞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.91,0:01:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,原來在這兒嗎，珊璞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.34,0:01:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然弄得自己這麼又冷又硬的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,沐絲你一個人在幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.53,0:01:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,珊璞，你在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.53,0:01:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,有事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.56,0:01:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,送外賣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.28,0:01:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我正在看書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,改你去送吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,客人想你去送嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,點名要我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.27,0:02:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,五町目的貓寺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.97,0:02:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.85,0:02:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,拉麵久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好奇怪都沒人在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,叫了外賣還這樣，真失禮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.28,0:02:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,有人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,等你好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,珊璞的囚禁之吻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,珊璞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.85,0:03:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,原來你在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,誰是珊璞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.15,0:03:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,戴眼鏡，眼鏡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.47,0:03:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我這麼忙的時候你還來打擾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.67,0:03:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.81,0:03:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,珊璞失蹤了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.58,0:03:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,早上，出去送外賣後，就沒回來過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,已經黃昏了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,弄得店裡忙死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.33,0:03:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不不，比起這個，我擔心珊璞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.08,0:03:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,珊璞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.81,0:03:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那，有去她送外賣的地方看過嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.98,0:03:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我忘了這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道你會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,總之，去叫外賣的那傢伙那裡看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.44,0:03:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,帶路吧，沐絲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.51,0:03:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯跟我一起去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.22,0:04:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起啊，亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.89,0:04:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不會是說謊的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.41,0:04:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,珊璞就是送外賣來這裡後沒回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.14,0:04:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.09,0:04:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.39,0:04:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡很久以前就是廢寺了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.63,0:04:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.29,0:04:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不是珊璞嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.74,0:04:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,珊璞，我找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你來接我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.11,0:04:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,住手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.36,0:04:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，珊璞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.83,0:04:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,磨磨擦擦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,笨死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬，回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.94,0:04:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.81,0:04:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我出不來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.82,0:04:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你開什麼玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,誰開玩笑啦，是真的出不來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我摟著不放，亂馬就不能出去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.47,0:05:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.94,0:05:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,別胡說，快放手啦，珊璞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.54,0:05:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.13,0:05:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我絕對不放手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.53,0:05:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,珊璞因為我的貓妖術，而被詛咒了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.92,0:05:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,明明老早以前就一直在找老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.17,0:05:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,可是一直都找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,走梅運一流的，傳說中的妖怪貓魔玲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不用你管
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是你幹的好事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我在這寺院裡張了結界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,珊璞是從這裡出不去的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡，你這妖怪貓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼把我的珊璞…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不管
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.24,0:05:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我要珊璞關在這裡，做我妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,死性不變，又是這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,珊璞，是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我會一輩子被關在跟妖怪貓一起生活\N這是我的命運啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，最惡劣的悲劇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有解除詛咒的方法嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.00,0:06:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一個方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.93,0:06:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有的，沒有的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,等你好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,怎樣，認輸了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.99,0:06:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,認輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.29,0:06:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不過已經太遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:07:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,從你一進來就被下詛咒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.45,0:07:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那詛咒只有我才能解除
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你已不能走出這寺院了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.23,0:07:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,留在這裡當我妻子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.67,0:07:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,別再打我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.99,0:07:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我，不做無用的抵抗了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你終於明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.67,0:07:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但是，如其做你妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我不如死了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.49,0:07:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你死了就什麼也沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.49,0:07:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯聽我話我就立即住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真是不會死心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.51,0:07:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我刺了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你想說什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.21,0:07:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我有一個，很喜歡的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.36,0:08:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,如果，我能跟那王子接吻的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.97,0:08:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你能把詛咒解除
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.87,0:08:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼我去投胎了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.82,0:08:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我聽你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那就快辦手續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.74,0:08:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.40,0:08:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我擦，我擦我擦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,王子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.16,0:08:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,快把我從這裡救出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.61,0:08:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,只是因為這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.78,0:08:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,來，亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.65,0:08:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,為了救我，快就跟我接吻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，那算什麼交易啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,做了的事已不能改了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼要用這種沒頭沒腦的方法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.31,0:09:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,連這也要我親口說出來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你別太過份了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,珊璞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.09,0:09:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在就來幫你解除詛咒\N（玉子）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.87,0:09:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,寫錯字啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡貓…！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.64,0:09:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.31,0:09:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了，亂馬？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,貓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,所以就拋下珊璞不管了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.23,0:09:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,也真不象話呢，亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.10,0:09:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你們這也算小小的格鬥家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,明天會去接她啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬，你給我好好的振作啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.49,0:09:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,貓啊，那只臭妖怪貓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.00,0:09:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,妖怪貓？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.17,0:10:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,又出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.45,0:10:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,明明老早以前就一直在找老婆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.59,0:10:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,可是一直都找不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.46,0:10:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,（以下相同）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.23,0:10:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,有件事還沒告訴你們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.21,0:10:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我也有事要問你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.98,0:10:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,解除詛咒的方法，真的只有接吻嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.58,0:10:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,接吻？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬怎麼老是有這些令人羡慕的事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸們給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.35,0:10:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.52,0:10:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,總之，怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.72,0:10:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,關於這事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.52,0:10:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.33,0:10:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚，在寺院的鐘響完一零八次之前\N不接吻的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.87,0:10:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,珊璞就會一生都出不了貓寺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.69,0:11:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,而已會完全變成貓，再也不能變回人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.42,0:11:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那可不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.63,0:11:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好可愛的小貓咪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.23,0:11:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚請你們別來寺院啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼粉？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬，沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.28,0:11:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡，竟然找到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.69,0:11:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,快來，救我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,珊璞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼好怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.37,0:11:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我一起建立一個幸福的家庭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.52,0:12:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,別這麼親熱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.96,0:12:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.63,0:12:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,珊璞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬，在那裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.38,0:12:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,珊璞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,太高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.99,0:12:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,珊璞，這是沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.19,0:12:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,今次我就跟你接吻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,這是沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.31,0:12:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我等會兒再來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了，亂馬？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.13,0:12:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,對貓來說木天蓼是最有效的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.48,0:12:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.85,0:12:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,在鐘聲響完前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.05,0:12:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,絕不讓你接近珊璞！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.53,0:12:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這真是悲劇性的發展啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.57,0:13:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.61,0:13:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,當響起第一零八下鐘聲珊璞就完全變成貓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.01,0:13:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我拷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,（亂馬的作戰，其之一）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,木天蓼衣服？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.63,0:13:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這衣服上塗了比我身上更多的木天蓼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你穿上這東西跳進去不就更加…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我趁小茜引開那些貓的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我就跟珊璞接吻解除妖怪貓的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.66,0:13:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.23,0:13:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我真是聰明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.25,0:14:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,這種事你自己去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.79,0:14:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.27,0:14:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,（亂馬的作戰，其之二）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.20,0:14:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,秋刀魚球？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.21,0:14:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,貓最喜歡圓滾滾，滾來滾去的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.11,0:14:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,而且這上面充滿了秋刀魚的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.06,0:14:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.54,0:14:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好，趁這機會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,珊璞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,來，珊璞，接受我的吻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.51,0:14:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,又是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,礙事，礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.09,0:14:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,（亂馬的作戰，其之三）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.30,0:14:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,（沒想到這步）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.20,0:15:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,沐絲這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛只差一步而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.69,0:15:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜，鐘響了多少下？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.86,0:15:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然不是很清楚，大概有四五十了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.90,0:15:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.34,0:15:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.34,0:15:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子根本無法接近珊璞在的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.41,0:15:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.61,0:15:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.38,0:15:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,可怕的貓魔鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼，吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是覺得啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,味道這麼重的衣服，應該立即換掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.94,0:15:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,又沒拿奇怪東西的話\N應該很輕易就能進去了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.52,0:15:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.82,0:15:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,蠢材
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,珊璞，我來救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.77,0:15:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.57,0:15:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你終於來到這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.41,0:15:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但是，我不會把珊璞交給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:16:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,想帶走她，就先打倒我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.92,0:16:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我還是怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.36,0:16:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.66,0:16:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡，妖怪貓你覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.84,0:16:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,來，珊璞，是你喜歡的王子的吻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.81,0:16:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,珊璞，到這種時候了你還…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.73,0:16:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我喜歡的王子的吻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.86,0:16:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,詛咒是解不開的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.23,0:16:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我不是說我是你喜歡的王子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.77,0:16:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼你不明白我的愛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.99,0:16:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.19,0:16:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,幫幫他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.77,0:16:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊這邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,快過來，快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.91,0:16:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是逗貓玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,來來來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.66,0:16:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧，來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.04,0:16:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好好，是好孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:17:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.65,0:17:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.11,0:17:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,來，趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,太高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,沐絲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.44,0:17:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,又是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,從剛才就老是阻礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.82,0:17:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.62,0:17:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼也要跟珊璞接吻的話就跟我決鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.79,0:17:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,珊璞不是說了不是我不要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.10,0:17:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.50,0:17:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我奉陪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,活該
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.73,0:17:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,來，珊璞，這次一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,珊璞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.53,0:18:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…閉上眼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你攪什麼氣氛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.99,0:18:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,做得好，天道茜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,逗貓玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好可怕的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.44,0:18:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,可是別以為這樣就贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡，亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬果然還是愛我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,竟敢當我透明！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.31,0:18:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,說回來都是你下了這麼無聊的詛咒才會這樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.07,0:18:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好，繼續討論吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,這是鐘聲！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.32,0:19:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕，我忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.74,0:19:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,珊璞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.91,0:19:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,貓耳朵…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.03,0:19:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.76,0:19:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,珊璞就快要完全變成貓了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.73,0:19:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然可恨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.15,0:19:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,只有今次我准你吻珊璞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.98,0:19:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬，快去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但是貓…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:19:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,都來到這一步了還這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,六十三，六十四，六十五，六十六
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.87,0:20:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他加快了打鐘的速度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.94,0:20:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.27,0:20:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.32,0:20:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.26,0:20:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你還等什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.93,0:20:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,七十四，七十五，七十六,七十七，七十八，七十九
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.21,0:20:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,小茜，沐絲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.24,0:20:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,在我背上猛踢一腳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.01,0:20:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,沒時間了，快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.35,0:20:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.76,0:20:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.24,0:20:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,太痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.78,0:20:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,第一零七下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,這下就是第一零八下了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.66,0:21:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.99,0:21:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,貓…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.73,0:21:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,詛咒解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.81,0:21:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,亂馬，再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.21,0:21:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡，亂馬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,竟敢和珊璞接吻！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.28,0:21:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡，可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,得救了真好呢，珊璞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.66,0:21:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我又失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.34,0:21:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要妻子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.41,0:23:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,遙遠的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.98,0:23:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我還以為已經模糊得看不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.52,0:23:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,可是你卻再次來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.76,0:23:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.52,0:23:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,請跟我私奔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.22,0:23:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,敬請期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.05,0:21:42.89,ED,,0,0,0,,留在我身邊 近得可以四目相投
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.94,0:21:47.14,ED,,0,0,0,,可是溫柔和笑臉卻交錯而過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.90,0:21:51.33,ED,,0,0,0,,你裝作沒發覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.50,0:21:55.76,ED,,0,0,0,,又趕著去惡作劇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.78,0:22:04.22,ED,,0,0,0,,即使如此 在那閃爍的山丘上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.65,0:22:19.63,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fsp1\pos(280,389.333)}斷斷續續的故事 只是單純的演戲
